title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - Airports and AIRAC - updates
description:
In this video we will have a look at the update which was released today which came as a surprise for a lot of us. The update contains the first batch of fixes as for airports as part of the World Hub tool which has been in beta for a few weeks now. In addition to this the AIRAC has received an update and is now on version 2402.
